-- Goldman Sachs Placing $260 Million of IG Group Shares for CVC, Terms Show
-- Sarah Jones
-- 2010-07-23T06:22:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/goldman-sachs-placing-260-million-of-ig-group-shares-for-cvc-terms-show.html

          
          
             Goldman Sachs Group Inc. is placing
3.6 million IG Group Plc shares for “several CVC-controlled
entities,” according to the terms obtained by Bloomberg News.  
 Goldman Sachs, a joint bookrunner, is offering about 17
million pounds worth of shares via an accelerated bookbuild
offering, the terms show.  
 The stock fell 1.1 percent to 475.5 pence yesterday.  
          
          


  


        